FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Unwrap the delightful details about our candy-coated app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of sweets does your app cover?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app covers a wide range of sweets, from chocolates and gummies to hard candies and artisanal confections. We're your one-stop shop for all things sugary and delicious!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How does the sweet recommendation feature work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Our smart algorithm takes into account your taste preferences, previous purchases, and current trends to suggest sweets you're likely to love. It's like having a personal candy concierge!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I track my candy consumption with this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Our app includes a fun and easy-to-use tracker that helps you log your sweet treats. It's a great way to balance indulgence with moderation.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Are there any features for people with dietary restrictions?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, we cater to various dietary needs. You can filter sweets by categories such as sugar-free, vegan, gluten-free, and nut-free to find treats that suit your specific requirements.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How often are new sweets added to the app's database?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We update our database weekly with new and exciting sweets from around the world. Our team of candy enthusiasts is always on the lookout for the latest and greatest confections to share with you!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What types of sweets does your app feature?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app showcases a wide variety of sweets, including chocolates, candies, pastries, and traditional desserts from around the world. We constantly update our collection to bring you the latest and most delicious treats.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How can I order sweets through the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Ordering is simple! Browse our selection, add items to your cart, and proceed to checkout. You can choose delivery options or pick up from select local partnered sweet shops. We ensure a smooth and sweet experience from selection to satisfaction.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Are there options for dietary restrictions?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! We offer a range of sweets for various dietary needs, including sugar-free, gluten-free, vegan, and nut-free options. Each item is clearly labeled, making it easy to find treats that suit your specific requirements.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I gift sweets to others using the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, you can! Our app features a gifting option where you can send delightful sweet surprises to your loved ones. Choose from our curated gift boxes or create a custom selection, add a personalized message, and we'll take care of the rest.
